26:48.960 --> 26:50.640
# As the best

26:50.640 --> 26:55.400
# Mum of all she wears the crown

26:55.400 --> 26:58.160
# A mother hen
watching all her chicks

26:58.160 --> 27:01.360
# Sassy old lady
full of tricks

27:01.360 --> 27:07.320
# It's a safe bet she'd never let
life get her down

